reviewText: I like this because I like to travel.  I'll admit, I like the Globe Trekker episodes better when the traveler is a woman, but this will do if you want to explore these exotic lands!
We love all of these travel dvds! The kids ask for more all the time. The travelers are funny and find interesting and odd things about each country
I loved the huge mata rays and whale sharks not to mention all the wide varity of culture on these islands is amazing.

I love Globe Trekker. This is a great intro to a place in the world we seldom see, the Indian Ocean.
I give this a 4 because I hate that in this day and age, we have to buy a physical product. Come on Globe Trekker.
I was looking for a more balanced view of different places and things to do and see but this was for the more adventurous at heart. Did not like it. Not enough variety. Quality was OK, though.
